            <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">Getting Started with Arsenal Vault: Your First 10 Minutes</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-6">A quick walkthrough of Arsenal Vault's core features. You'll add your first firearm, explore the dashboard, and understand the basics before your coffee gets cold.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
